## Security

- All packages are managed through devenv.nix — do not run raw install commands outside the Nix shell.
- Never commit secrets, tokens, or credentials. The pre-commit hook `ripsecrets` blocks accidental leaks.
- Lock files must always be committed. Never delete or regenerate lock files without review.
